    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel 1/3 of the <strong>Italian hard cheese</strong> until you end up with a pile of cheese shavings</p><p>Grate the <strong>remaining Italian hard cheese</strong> finely</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
