    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once slightly thickened, add the <strong>hake fillets</strong> to the pan and top with the <strong>spinach</strong></p><p>Cook, covered, for 5-6 min or until the fish is cooked through and the spinach has wilted – this is your <strong>tangy tomato hake</strong></p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked once it turns opaque and flakes easily</p>",
